summary: Middle-aged dentist Biff Grimes reminisces about his unrequited love for beautiful Virginia Brush and her husband Hugo, his ex-friend, who betrayed him.
cast: Gary Cooper|Fay Wray|Frances Fuller|Roscoe Karns|Neil Hamilton|Jane Darwell|Clara Blandick|James Bradbury Jr.|Ed Brady|James P. Burtis|A.S. 'Pop' Byron|Jack Rube Clifford|Robert Homans|Carmencita Johnson|Gus Leonard|Jim Mason|Russ Powell|Harry Schultz|Frank Sheridan|John St. Clair
title: La mujer preferida
